{"tid":1866657,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總統Donald Trump 特朗普批評民主黨惡毒而卑鄙　形容科米為災難","createTime":"2020-02-06T22:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T22:30:12.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3640efa649ebd28e1906397b15c7ac315aee515d","tid":1866657,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:25:18.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在參議院否決彈劾之後，在白宮向民主黨人嚴詞反擊，批評民主黨「惡毒而卑鄙」，令他在彈劾案的過程中，感覺就像「落地獄」一樣。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱，由他宣布參選總統開始，就一直受獵巫行動的政治迫害，歷時三年，認為另一位總統不應該再有相同的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又批評被他解僱的聯邦調查局前局長科米，形容他是一個災難，指如果沒有將他解僱，自己今日可能不能在站在白宮之内。他又形容民主黨的國會議長波洛西，和眾議院情報委員會主席希夫「恐怖」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507137-20200207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507137-20200207.htm&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWTRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=6f1bd082\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507137-20200207.htm&h=ee4ff877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507137-20200207.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b7061cd340a2ea9ebc7ef373bbcf0078c3bfff64","tid":1866657,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c4ffe6bb5e86cb31c27de7709e6f213e7f855de","tid":1866657,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmEb6EG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmEb6EG.jpg&h=d4adb4c9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}